<br />\n3. 德國 - 柏林<br />\n4. 英國 - 倫敦、格拉斯哥<br />\n5.  澳洲 - 布里斯本 、墨爾本、悉民<br />\n6. 紐西蘭 - 奧克蘭、基督城<br />\n7. 比利時 - 布魯塞爾<br />\n8. 加拿大 - 溫哥華<br />\n<br />\n至於各地詳情，請留意 &ldquo;Fight for Freedom. Stand with Hong Kong.&rdquo; Facebook page持續更新。<br />\n<br />\n最後，民集團隊更會喺黎緊星期日1.12 舉辦《天下制裁集會》為1.19集定氣，打響頭炮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🔥正牌攬炒Channel🔥<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/StirFryChannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStirFryChannel&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyD11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=25d47095\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/StirFryChannel</a><br />\n<br />\n#國際戰線 #本土戰線 #清算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5jxAQHO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5jxAQHO.jpg&h=b8c68f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UpXUmPw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUpXUmPw.jpg&h=8fa26607&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ebbc7ca54970bc2cda22e80970da1fbab2055eb","tid":1822483,"uid":6142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:52:36.000Z","msg":"香港影響世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868220942529ab37bedc2e53c7c44c1be9e0e26c","tid":1822483,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:52:57.000Z","msg":"Bring yourself back online"},{"pid":"517248df9a30869b3466acbddca6c54a29bbfc63","tid":1822483,"uid":63846,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f5901500c121a086c38e36401f5feba2bca168cf","tid":1822483,"uid":41998,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:50:54.000Z","msg":"《西部世界3》新預告中，見到一切世界大事，都是源於「2019年6月12日，分歧：香港&ndash;政治動盪，大規模抗議。」之後，由於連鎖效應，世界各地都發生假設性的重大事故<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:53:13.000Z","msg":"陳同佳效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},